In [5]:
tol_bri <- c('#0077BB','#33BBEE','#009988','#EE7733','#CC3311','#EE3377','#BBBBBB')
cluster_df3 <- node_df %>% group_by(mc) %>% summarize(mc_seq_n=n(),mc_rep_n=n_distinct(repname_RM),mc_fam_n=n_distinct(repname_RM4))
node_df2 <- merge(node_df,cluster_df3,by="mc")
node_df2$size_bin <- as.factor(ifelse(node_df2$mc_seq_n <= 10,'0-10',
                            ifelse(node_df2$mc_seq_n <= 1000, '11-1000',
                                  ifelse(node_df2$mc_seq_n <= 2000,'1001-2000',
                                         ifelse(node_df2$mc_seq_n <=5000,'2001-5000','>5000')))))

plot_c <- node_df2 %>%
          mutate(size_bin = fct_relevel(size_bin, 
            "0-10", "11-1000", "1001-2000", 
            "2001-5000",">5000")) %>%
            ggplot(aes(factor(mc_rep_n))) + geom_bar(width = 0.9)+
            theme_minimal() + geom_bar(aes(fill=size_bin))+xlab('Number of Families per Cluster')+
            ylab("Sequence Count") + scale_fill_manual(values=tol_bri,name="cluster size")+
            theme(legend.position='bottom',text=element_text(size=20,family="Times New Roman"))
plot_c

In [6]:
cluster_df3 <- node_df %>% group_by(mc) %>% summarize(seq_n=n(),rep_n=n_distinct(repname_RM),fam_n=n_distinct(repname_RM4))
cluster_df3$size_bin <- as.factor(ifelse(cluster_df3$seq_n <= 2,'2',
                            ifelse(cluster_df3$seq_n <= 10, '3-10','>10')))
tol_bri <- c('#0077BB','#33BBEE','#009988','#EE7733','#CC3311','#EE3377','#BBBBBB')

plot_d <- ggplot(cluster_df3,aes(factor(rep_n)))+geom_bar(width = 0.9)+
        theme_minimal() + geom_bar(aes(fill=size_bin))+xlab('Number of Families per Cluster')+
        ylab("Cluster Count") + scale_fill_manual(values=tol_bri,name="cluster size")+
        theme(legend.position='bottom',text=element_text(size=20,family="Times New Roman"))
plot_d
